Rank 3: The Time Surplus Reallocation (Move 8) — Flipped student from panic to dominance. 51-minute surplus = game-changer. 10/10 impact.
Rank 4: The Psychological Anchor (Move 9) — Every panic thought → exploitable pattern. Enabled sustained confidence. 9/10 impact.
Rank 5: The Calculus Bypass (Move 2) — 8 marks. No conceptual math required. 9/10 impact.
Rank 6: The Z-Factor Verification (Move 6) — Catches the #1 cubic EOS error in 10 seconds. 8/10 impact.
Rank 7: The Control Volume Reframe (Move 5) — Simplifies multi-step thermodynamics. 7/10 impact.
Rank 8: The FX-82MS Chunking (Move 3) — Hardware adaptation. 7/10 impact.
Rank 9: The 2000-Divisor (Move 4) — Prevents unit-trap failure on Target 2.1. 6/10 impact (prevents 4 marks loss, less critical than the 7/8-mark targets).

